thingy, this worked perfectly. I'm running Win 7 Ultimate, and have a legal version of Office Pro 2010 installed. I followed the instructions and copied the mso.dll to both locations. After opening Visio I was not prompted to activate. I clicked Help, Activate Product and was pleasantly surprised to see a popup that the product was already activated.
